{
  "stem": "14060.8",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he literally appointed a kangaroo court of these German political prisoners.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They drew on maybe one or two others.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know exactly who they consisted of.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this kangaroo court, so to speak, went on night after night, one after the other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And if there was a single accusing person who said that I have seen that this-and-this person, this guy has either killed or even maimed beyond sort of recovery, which meant death for that person, that guy was next morning amongst the dead on the-- not the truck, but the sort of a vehicle or whatever they were hanging around where they put all the dead people.",
      "word_count": 67
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And nobody knew about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was, to my mind, an element of justice-- maybe rough justice-- but certainly justice carried out, because it was a reasonably organized camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And believe you me, these people didn't deserve to live.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was absolutely nobody had any pity.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody said that they-- they-- have extended and increased the number of deaths then was-- than-- then the Germans thought was necessary.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Germans didn't care if one prisoner killed another one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had less one to worry about, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were literally inhumane.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember there was a gypsy blockalteste in-- in-- in-- in-- in-- Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I knew him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I didn't know what he was doing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were there for five days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was one of them who they put away with.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is just the sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyway, now, coming back the day I just mentioned that what happened the day before the liberation.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Next morning at 10 o'clock they reinstated the same method of trying to get the rest of the Jews out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
